---
title: Pork Schnitzel & BBQ-Sriracha Sauce with Garlic Crushed Potatoes & Apple Slaw
description: It’s a twist on pork schnitzel, we’re combining sriracha with BBQ sauce so the schnitzels are extra mouth-watering
when this sauce is drizzled over. This dish becomes more alluring when you catch the scent of garlic-infused potato,
crushed so that you can’t miss them on the plate.

